Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.50,0:00:01.68,Default,,0,0,0,,《法外情真》前情提要\N{\fs12}Previously the The Guardian.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.60,0:00:03.68,Default,,0,0,0,,我怀孕了\N{\fs12}I'm pregnant.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.54,0:00:05.50,Default,,0,0,0,,这是你想要的吗\N{\fs12}This is what you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.50,0:00:06.86,Default,,0,0,0,,不  我不想\N{\fs12}No, I don't wanna be.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.00,0:00:08.18,Default,,0,0,0,,你想作爸爸吗\N{\fs12}Do you wanna be a father?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.60,0:00:15.36,Default,,0,0,0,,我不想结婚只是因为我怀孕了\N{\fs12}I don't wanna get married just because I'm pregnant.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.36,0:00:17.36,Default,,0,0,0,,呃  我不在乎你嫁不嫁给我\N{\fs12}uh I don't care if you don't want to marry me.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.36,0:00:18.76,Default,,0,0,0,,没关系的  我只是\N{\fs12}It's alright, I just...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.76,0:00:20.22,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道我做好了作父亲的准备\N{\fs12}I know that I'm ready to be a father.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.38,0:00:21.38,Default,,0,0,0,,你的伴儿呢\N{\fs12}Where's your date?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.38,0:00:22.58,Default,,0,0,0,,她走了\N{\fs12}She left.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.72,0:01:03.25,Default,,0,0,0,,早上好  法林先生\N{\fs12}Morning, Mr. Fallin.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.37,0:01:05.90,Default,,0,0,0,,明天见  法林先生\N{\fs12}See you tomorrow, Mr. Fallin.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.20,0:01:32.66,Default,,0,0,0,,- 尼古拉斯  - 跟医生谈得怎么样\N{\fs12}- Nicholas. - How did it go with the doctor?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.78,0:01:35.11,Default,,0,0,0,,查出来我的动脉里有堵塞\N{\fs12}Evidently I've got a little blockage.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.17,0:01:37.15,Default,,0,0,0,,有多少\N{\fs12}Yeah? How much?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.28,0:01:40.98,Default,,0,0,0,,五条动脉有四条有堵塞  百分之八十五\N{\fs12}Four out of five arteries, 85 percent.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.11,0:01:43.05,Default,,0,0,0,,- 需要做手术吗  - 是的\N{\fs12}- So you need surgery? - Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.18,0:01:45.57,Default,,0,0,0,,- 那什么时候做手术  - 我不知道\N{\fs12}- Well, when you gonna go in? - I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.70,0:01:46.88,Default,,0,0,0,,我想  几个月后吧\N{\fs12}A few months, I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.01,0:01:48.54,Default,,0,0,0,,- 几个月  - 是的\N{\fs12}- A few months? - Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.67,0:01:49.91,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么现在不做\N{\fs12}Why not right now?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.04,0:01:52.97,Default,,0,0,0,,因为  第一  我们现在正在忙奥尼克斯・弗莱特公司合并的事\N{\fs12}Well, in the first place, we're right in the middle of that Onyx Freight merger.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.10,0:01:54.92,Default,,0,0,0,,爸  那是我的事情  我一个人可以搞定\N{\fs12}Oh, Dad, that's my deal. I can take care of that alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.04,0:01:57.95,Default,,0,0,0,,尼古拉斯  我们已经和詹姆斯・富勒合作很久了了\N{\fs12}Nicholas, we've been working with James Fuller for a long time now.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.07,0:01:59.38,Default,,0,0,0,,这事儿比较棘手\N{\fs12}That's a little tricky.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.51,0:02:02.13,Default,,0,0,0,,你不能因为富勒就先不做手术了啊\N{\fs12}You shouldn't let Fuller stop you from having the surgery.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.25,0:02:05.44,Default,,0,0,0,,问题是  我想让胡特医生给我做手术\N{\fs12}Well, the real problem is that surgeon I want, Dr. Hutter?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.57,0:02:08.25,Default,,0,0,0,,- 哦  - 但是在接下来的八周  他都在曼谷\N{\fs12}- Right. - Bangkok for the next eight weeks.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.38,0:02:09.59,Default,,0,0,0,,你要等他回来吗\N{\fs12}Are you're going to wait for him to get back?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.72,0:02:10.90,Default,,0,0,0,,是的\N{\fs12}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.18,0:03:22.30,Default,,0,0,0,,尼克\N{\fs12}Nick.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.43,0:03:23.72,Default,,0,0,0,,那是什么\N{\fs12}What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.84,0:03:26.47,Default,,0,0,0,,这是客户送的一幅画\N{\fs12}Oh, it's just a picture from a client.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.53,0:03:28.88,Default,,0,0,0,,好有爱\N{\fs12}Oh, that's sweet.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.00,0:03:30.86,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊\N{\fs12}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.99,0:03:34.42,Default,,0,0,0,,我找到了一个房地产经纪人\N{\fs12}So, I think I found a realtor.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.55,0:03:37.14,Default,,0,0,0,,我很喜欢她  她叫潘妮\N{\fs12}A realtor that I like. Her name's Penny.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.27,0:03:39.74,Default,,0,0,0,,她主要在莎迪赛德和东方自由工作\N{\fs12}She works primarily in Shadyside and East Liberty.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.87,0:03:41.37,Default,,0,0,0,,她就是我们要找的人\N{\fs12}She knows exactly what we're looking for.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.50,0:03:42.40,Default,,0,0,0,,好的\N{\fs12}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.52,0:03:44.23,Default,,0,0,0,,而且她已经找到了几个很棒的地方  所以\N{\fs12}And she's already found some great places, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.35,0:03:45.83,Default,,0,0,0,,我来看看你什么时候有空\N{\fs12}I just wanted to check your schedule.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.95,0:03:48.30,Default,,0,0,0,,我随时都行\N{\fs12}Well...whenever you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.42,0:03:51.18,Default,,0,0,0,,- 随时吗  - 随时\N{\fs12}- Whenever? - Whenever.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.81,0:03:53.81,Default,,0,0,0,,那好\N{\fs12}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.72,0:04:18.29,Default,,0,0,0,,你好  我是尼克・法林\N{\fs12}Hi, this is Nick Fallin.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.42,0:04:20.53,Default,,0,0,0,,你是贝蒂吗  你好\N{\fs12}ls this Betty? Yeah, hi.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.66,0:04:23.39,Default,,0,0,0,,加里森医生说你手里有份\N{\fs12}Dr. Garrison said that you would have a list
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.51,0:04:26.33,Default,,0,0,0,,可以给我父亲做手术的心脏外科医生名单\N{\fs12}of available heart surgeons for my father.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.93,0:04:31.59,Default,,0,0,0,,好的  好的  谢谢你  贝蒂  谢谢\N{\fs12}Okay. Okay. Well, thank you, Betty. I appreciate it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.29,0:04:35.34,Default,,0,0,0,,有人生病了吗\N{\fs12}ls someone sick?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.46,0:04:38.38,Default,,0,0,0,,一个朋友  心脏有点问题\N{\fs12}Just a friend. He has a heart problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.51,0:04:41.49,Default,,0,0,0,,我15岁的时候我爸因为心脏病发作去世了\N{\fs12}Oh. My dad died of a heart attack when I was 15.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.62,0:04:43.83,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉\N{\fs12}I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.12,0:04:52.68,Default,,0,0,0,,我想说的是  我被分到了一个叫克里斯托弗・拉普的孩子的案子\N{\fs12}Anyway, I was just assigned to this kid, Christopher Rapp.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.80,0:04:55.24,Default,,0,0,0,,露露说  去年他是你的客户\N{\fs12}Lulu said that he was your client Iast year.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.36,0:04:56.62,Default,,0,0,0,,不记得了\N{\fs12}Don't remember him.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.74,0:04:59.34,Default,,0,0,0,,他在训练营遇到了麻烦\N{\fs12}Well, he's in some trouble over at Summit Boot Camp.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.91,0:05:02.80,Default,,0,0,0,,克里斯在两个月前被安置到了训练营\N{\fs12}Chris was placed at Summit two months ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.93,0:05:03.83,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么\N{\fs12}Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.95,0:05:05.36,Default,,0,0,0,,跟一个八岁的女生发生了一些过节\N{\fs12}Had a problem with an eight-year-old girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.49,0:05:06.90,Default,,0,0,0,,- 什么过节？  - 很显然  他摸了那个女孩\N{\fs12}- Problem? - Apparently he touched her.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.03,0:05:08.86,Default,,0,0,0,,- 好吧  - 所以他不是被抓到训练营就是在教管所\N{\fs12}- Okay. - So it was either Summit or Juvie.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.98,0:05:10.49,Default,,0,0,0,,- 他几岁了  - 十五岁\N{\fs12}- How old is he? - 15.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.62,0:05:13.60,Default,,0,0,0,,上周他惹了麻烦  在食堂打架斗殴\N{\fs12}Last week he got into some trouble, started a fire in the mess hall.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.73,0:05:15.91,Default,,0,0,0,,训练营的头就把他锁在柜子里关了两天\N{\fs12}Head of the camp locked him in a closet for two days.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.04,0:05:17.41,Default,,0,0,0,,这就是我们这次过来的原因\N{\fs12}That's why we're here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.54,0:05:19.40,Default,,0,0,0,,走  集合\N{\fs12}Let's go! Fall in!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.53,0:05:22.22,Default,,0,0,0,,我们可没那么多时间  各位先生  集合  排好队\N{\fs12}We don't have all day, gentlemen! Let's go! Line up!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.28,0:05:24.95,Default,,0,0,0,,快走  快走\N{\fs12}Move it! Come on, gentlemen!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.29,0:05:29.40,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你好  法林先生  - 你好  克里斯\N{\fs12}- Hey, Mr. Fallin. - Hey, Chris.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.53,0:05:30.42,Default,,0,0,0,,你是谁\N{\fs12}Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.55,0:05:34.14,Default,,0,0,0,,我叫苏珊娜・佩尔  我被分配和法林先生一起参与你的案子\N{\fs12}I am Suzanne Pell. I'm assigned to your case with Mr. Fallin.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.27,0:05:36.55,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你很漂亮  - 谢谢\N{\fs12}- You're really pretty. - Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.67,0:05:38.21,Default,,0,0,0,,不用谢\N{\fs12}That's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.34,0:05:39.88,Default,,0,0,0,,坐吧\N{\fs12}Have a seat.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.35,0:05:58.18,Default,,0,0,0,,额  苏珊娜  我和他单独聊一会儿吧\N{\fs12}Uh, Suzanne, can you give us a minute?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.30,0:05:59.91,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢\N{\fs12}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.14,0:06:10.06,Default,,0,0,0,,我听说你在食堂打架了\N{\fs12}So I heard you started a fire.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.19,0:06:12.82,Default,,0,0,0,,额\N{\fs12}Uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.95,0:06:16.51,Default,,0,0,0,,我妈过生日  他们都不让我见见我妈\N{\fs12}Well, they wouldn't let me see my mom for her birthday.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.63,0:06:18.75,Default,,0,0,0,,我妈过生日  我一定要陪她的\N{\fs12}I always see my mom for her birthday.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.88,0:06:20.96,Default,,0,0,0,,一定\N{\fs12}Always.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.09,0:06:22.59,Default,,0,0,0,,在这里苦不苦啊\N{\fs12}You having a hard time here?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.72,0:06:24.74,Default,,0,0,0,,苦\N{\fs12}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.87,0:06:27.76,Default,,0,0,0,,虽然这里有很酷的人\N{\fs12}I mean, there are some cool people here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.88,0:06:29.61,Default,,0,0,0,,但是这里大部分的人都不好\N{\fs12}Mostly not.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.74,0:06:32.05,Default,,0,0,0,,我也挺喜欢这里的这位辅导员的\N{\fs12}And the counselors, I like a few of them,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.18,0:06:35.64,Default,,0,0,0,,但是有几个辅导员让我们打架  然后他们赌我们谁赢谁输\N{\fs12}but a couple a guys make us fight, and they bet on us.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.76,0:06:38.88,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你举报了吗  - 只跟你们说了\N{\fs12}- Did you report this? - Just to you guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.00,0:06:41.47,Default,,0,0,0,,大部分孩子都讨厌我\N{\fs12}I mean, most of the kids hate me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.60,0:06:44.87,Default,,0,0,0,,有一次他们还让我吃泥巴\N{\fs12}They made me eat mud once.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.99,0:06:46.89,Default,,0,0,0,,他们偷我的鞋\N{\fs12}They stole my shoes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.01,0:06:49.32,Default,,0,0,0,,我都能接受  但是\N{\fs12}And I can take that, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.45,0:06:53.75,Default,,0,0,0,,但是  那次辅导员把我锁在柜子里\N{\fs12}But when that counselor did that thing, locked me in the closet,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.87,0:06:55.79,Default,,0,0,0,,我好想见我妈\N{\fs12}I just wanted to see my mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.20,0:07:00.22,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧  克里斯  我看看我能做点儿什么\N{\fs12}All right, Chris. Well, I'll see what I can do.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.34,0:07:02.91,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你能帮我离开这里吗  - 我会尽力\N{\fs12}- You'll get me out of here? - I'll see what I can do.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.04,0:07:04.51,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢你\N{\fs12}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.10,0:07:09.41,Default,,0,0,0,,像我之前说的那样\N{\fs12}Like I said before.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.54,0:07:12.39,Default,,0,0,0,,鉴于当时的情况  那样处罚他是合理的\N{\fs12}He was punished appropriately, given the circumstances.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.52,0:07:15.21,Default,,0,0,0,,你有没有把他锁在柜子里\N{\fs12}Did you lock him in a closet?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.68,0:07:20.12,Default,,0,0,0,,他只是被合理地惩罚了\N{\fs12}He was punished appropriately.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.99,0:07:26.49,Default,,0,0,0,,- 真是讲不通  - 是啊\N{\fs12}- What a tool. - Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.62,0:07:29.00,Default,,0,0,0,,我们把孩子救出来吧\N{\fs12}Well, you know, let's try and get this kid out of here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.12,0:07:30.47,Default,,0,0,0,,他们会把他送到教管所的\N{\fs12}They'll just send him to Juvie.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.59,0:07:32.68,Default,,0,0,0,,也许我们可以好好跟法官谈一谈\N{\fs12}Well, maybe we can work something out with the judge.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.81,0:07:34.76,Default,,0,0,0,,好的\N{\fs12}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.89,0:07:36.40,Default,,0,0,0,,- 尼克  - 什么事\N{\fs12}- Nick? - Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.52,0:07:38.99,Default,,0,0,0,,那天聚餐的晚上\N{\fs12}About the other night at the party.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.12,0:07:43.42,Default,,0,0,0,,就那样发生了  我不是有意让你不舒服的\N{\fs12}It just happened, and I didn't mean to make you feel uncomfortable.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.54,0:07:46.78,Default,,0,0,0,,我不是那种随随便便  在衣帽间亲男人的女人\N{\fs12}I don't exactly go around kissing men in coat rooms.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.38,0:07:54.98,Default,,0,0,0,,爸\N{\fs12}Dad?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.57,0:08:16.26,Default,,0,0,0,,嗨  尼克\N{\fs12}Hey, Nick.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.32,0:08:17.61,Default,,0,0,0,,嗨\N{\fs12}Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.73,0:08:20.11,Default,,0,0,0,,- 有事吗  - 没事\N{\fs12}- What's up? - Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.48,0:08:24.37,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你在这边吃吗  - 还没\N{\fs12}- You eating over? - No.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.96,0:08:33.40,Default,,0,0,0,,我爸在家吗\N{\fs12}ls my dad here?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.53,0:08:34.75,Default,,0,0,0,,在的\N{\fs12}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.88,0:08:37.19,Default,,0,0,0,,- 嗨  - 嗨\N{\fs12}- Hey. - Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.31,0:08:38.88,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我就说  好像听到你的声音了  - 是啊\N{\fs12}- Thought I heard you. - Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.01,0:08:41.61,Default,,0,0,0,,香农  我想跟我爸单独说两句\N{\fs12}Uh, Shannon, I have to speak with my dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.86,0:08:44.33,Default,,0,0,0,,工作的事情吗\N{\fs12}Work stuff?
