Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.50,0:09:08.88,Default,,0,0,0,,苏格兰威士忌\N{\fs12}Scotch.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.01,0:09:11.00,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊\N{\fs12}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.12,0:09:13.24,Default,,0,0,0,,我今天去找过加里森医生了\N{\fs12}I went to see Dr. Garrison today.
