Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.00,0:09:24.23,Default,,0,0,0,,他还说胡特医生是东海岸最好都的心脏外科医生呢\N{\fs12}He also thinks Dr. Hutter is the best heart surgeon on the East Coast.
