Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.82,0:09:42.44,Default,,0,0,0,,我这里有份名单  上面有三个医生 他们都有时间做手术并且口碑都不错\N{\fs12}I have a list here of three surgeons, all available and all highly recommended.
