Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.68,0:09:55.19,Default,,0,0,0,,约翰・西格尔  我之前有跟他一起打过网球\N{\fs12}John Siegel. I used to play tennis with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.31,0:09:56.85,Default,,0,0,0,,我一直不喜欢他\N{\fs12}I never liked the guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.98,0:09:58.81,Default,,0,0,0,,那么  就剩下帕特里夏・德里斯科尔了\N{\fs12}Well, then it's Patricia Driscoll.
