Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.15,0:11:17.07,Default,,0,0,0,,而且主卧太棒了  你不觉得吗\N{\fs12}and the master bedroom is spectacular, don't you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.19,0:11:20.30,Default,,0,0,0,,所以  你喜欢吗\N{\fs12}So, how do you like it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.40,0:11:26.52,Default,,0,0,0,,你有没有四处转转\N{\fs12}Well, have you looked around?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.64,0:11:27.99,Default,,0,0,0,,有啊\N{\fs12}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.18,0:11:31.13,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道吗  他们这套房子唯一不足的地方就是\N{\fs12}You know, the only mistake that they made with this house
