Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.53,0:11:37.22,Default,,0,0,0,,但是我在想  你可以把那个柜子敲掉  然后放一个淋浴室\N{\fs12}But I was thinking, you could knock that closet out and put a half-bath in.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.35,0:11:39.85,Default,,0,0,0,,好  我能跟你说说我是怎么想的吗\N{\fs12}Yeah, can I tell you what I'm thinking about,
