Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.34,0:11:54.98,Default,,0,0,0,,好的\N{\fs12}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.40,0:12:31.97,Default,,0,0,0,,- 嗨  - 你是尼克吗\N{\fs12}- Hi. - You're Nick?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.09,0:12:34.33,Default,,0,0,0,,你是斯科尔医生吗  谢谢你能见我\N{\fs12}Dr. Driscoll? Thanks for your time.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.45,0:12:35.44,Default,,0,0,0,,我可以为你做什么\N{\fs12}What can I do for you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.57,0:12:38.29,Default,,0,0,0,,关于我父亲伯顿・法林  我有几个问题想要请教你\N{\fs12}I just wanted to ask you some questions about my father, Burton Fallin.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.41,0:12:40.36,Default,,0,0,0,,我看过他的病历了  他需要手术\N{\fs12}I've seen his chart. He needs surgery.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.49,0:12:42.31,Default,,0,0,0,,这样的手术你做过几次\N{\fs12}How many of these procedures have you performed?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.44,0:12:43.33,Default,,0,0,0,,150次\N{\fs12}150.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.46,0:12:45.66,Default,,0,0,0,,希望你不要介意  我能问下你做这种手术的成功率是多少吗\N{\fs12}lf you don't mind my asking, what is your success rate?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.79,0:12:48.28,Default,,0,0,0,,这是心脏手术  但是我的死亡率\N{\fs12}lt's heart surgery, but my fatality rate
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.41,0:12:50.54,Default,,0,0,0,,与其他顶级胸外科医生的死亡率一样\N{\fs12}is consistent with every other top thoracic surgeon.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.67,0:12:52.20,Default,,0,0,0,,你觉得胡特医生怎么样\N{\fs12}What do you think of Dr. Hutter?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.33,0:12:54.76,Default,,0,0,0,,我觉得他很厉害  我就是他教的\N{\fs12}I think he's good. He trained me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.89,0:12:58.15,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你是想问我有没有把握做这个手术  我的答案是非常有把握\N{\fs12}lf you're asking if I can handle it, my answer is absolutely.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.27,0:13:00.54,Default,,0,0,0,,太棒了  谢谢\N{\fs12}Great. Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.85,0:13:03.12,Default,,0,0,0,,爸\N{\fs12}Dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.25,0:13:04.46,Default,,0,0,0,,- 嗨  - 嗨\N{\fs12}- Hey. - Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.59,0:13:07.82,Default,,0,0,0,,我刚才去见了斯科尔医生  她很厉害\N{\fs12}I just met with Dr. Driscoll. She's very impressive.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.94,0:13:10.43,Default,,0,0,0,,我在想你能不能见见她\N{\fs12}You know, I thought maybe if you just met with her--
