Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.11,0:13:42.84,Default,,0,0,0,,那就让警察去调查吧\N{\fs12}Then let the state look into it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.96,0:13:44.21,Default,,0,0,0,,但是这样对我的当事人没有任何帮助\N{\fs12}But that doesn't help my client, Your Honor.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.34,0:13:46.70,Default,,0,0,0,,你是在说让我把他送到教改所吗\N{\fs12}You're asking me to send your client to Juvenile Detention?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.83,0:13:49.83,Default,,0,0,0,,不是  我是在请求您帮他找到一个适合他的地方\N{\fs12}No, I'm asking you to let me find him an appropriate placement.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.84,0:13:53.95,Default,,0,0,0,,这已经是我第二次看到你当事人的案子了\N{\fs12}Your client has been in front of me twice.
