Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.00,0:14:45.92,Default,,0,0,0,,你想要吗\N{\fs12}Do you want it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.05,0:14:48.67,Default,,0,0,0,,不是  我只是觉得那套房子很适合我们俩  还有我们的宝宝\N{\fs12}No, I just think it really works for us... with the baby.
