Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.39,0:16:03.01,Default,,0,0,0,,但是我们有工作\N{\fs12}Yeah, but we're both working.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.14,0:16:07.68,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯  你知道  你的工资\N{\fs12}Well, you know, you're income's, uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.80,0:16:11.89,Default,,0,0,0,,我们都想要这太房子  所以为什么不我把房子买下  然后你跟我住呢\N{\fs12}We both want it. So why don't I just buy it, and we can live here together?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.02,0:16:13.26,Default,,0,0,0,,不  我想和你一起买\N{\fs12}No, I want to buy it with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.39,0:16:14.54,Default,,0,0,0,,你不想结婚\N{\fs12}You don't want to get married,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.66,0:16:17.86,Default,,0,0,0,,但是你想跟我一起还贷款\N{\fs12}but you want to get into a 30-year mortgage with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.64,0:16:44.20,Default,,0,0,0,,谁啊\N{\fs12}Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.32,0:16:48.80,Default,,0,0,0,,他伤得很严重吗\N{\fs12}How badly hurt is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.92,0:16:52.31,Default,,0,0,0,,好的  你现在在训练营吗\N{\fs12}Right. Are you there at Summit now?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.37,0:16:55.27,Default,,0,0,0,,好的  你需要我去吗\N{\fs12}Okay. Do you need me?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.40,0:16:57.00,Default,,0,0,0,,好的\N{\fs12}Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.12,0:16:58.59,Default,,0,0,0,,好的  明天卢茨法官那边见面\N{\fs12}All right, tomorrow at Judge Lutz's.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.72,0:17:00.99,Default,,0,0,0,,好的  再见\N{\fs12}Yeah. Bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.35,0:17:04.72,Default,,0,0,0,,是谁啊\N{\fs12}Who was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.85,0:17:06.64,Default,,0,0,0,,苏珊娜・佩尔\N{\fs12}Suzanne Pell.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.88,0:17:09.99,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么了\N{\fs12}What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.12,0:17:14.56,Default,,0,0,0,,一个客户  克里斯・拉普  想要逃出训练营\N{\fs12}A client, Chris Rapp, he tried to escape from Summit.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.68,0:17:17.40,Default,,0,0,0,,被辅导员抓到了  揍了一顿\N{\fs12}Counselor that caught him beat him up.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.52,0:17:19.44,Default,,0,0,0,,可怜的孩子\N{\fs12}Poor kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.57,0:17:21.48,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊\N{\fs12}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.56,0:17:27.10,Default,,0,0,0,,尼克  关于房子\N{\fs12}You know, Nick, about the house...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.23,0:17:29.46,Default,,0,0,0,,都是为了孩子  对吗  为了我们的孩子\N{\fs12}lt's for the baby, right? Our baby.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.59,0:17:32.37,Default,,0,0,0,,所以我想我们应该\N{\fs12}So that's why I think that we really should just-
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.77,0:17:37.83,Default,,0,0,0,,什么事\N{\fs12}Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.95,0:17:41.37,Default,,0,0,0,,苏珊娜・佩尔真的有必要在半夜三点给你打电话吗\N{\fs12}Does Suzanne Pell really need you at 3:OO in the morning?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.50,0:17:43.00,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧\N{\fs12}All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.44,0:17:52.00,Default,,0,0,0,,- 嗨  - 嗨\N{\fs12}- Hey. - Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.13,0:17:53.53,Default,,0,0,0,,我跟加里森医生谈过了\N{\fs12}I spoke to Dr. Garrison.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.66,0:17:56.31,Default,,0,0,0,,好消息事这不是心脏病发作\N{\fs12}Good news is it wasn't a heart attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.44,0:17:58.71,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊  我也觉得不是\N{\fs12}Yeah, I didn't think so.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.83,0:18:03.15,Default,,0,0,0,,我这是上楼去拿香烟\N{\fs12}Just walking up the stairs to get some cigarettes and...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.27,0:18:05.70,Default,,0,0,0,,突然就呼吸不过来了\N{\fs12}I couldn't get my breath.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.82,0:18:09.63,Default,,0,0,0,,胸口紧绷\N{\fs12}Tightness in the chest.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.75,0:18:13.90,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道吗  德里斯科尔医生  呃\N{\fs12}You know, this Dr. Driscoll, um...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.03,0:18:18.47,Default,,0,0,0,,她就是胡特医生教出来的  而且她有空\N{\fs12}She was trained by Dr. Hutter, and she's available.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.59,0:18:20.61,Default,,0,0,0,,是\N{\fs12}Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.73,0:18:22.52,Default,,0,0,0,,你要不要做手术\N{\fs12}You want to do it?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.65,0:18:26.00,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧  我觉得可以做了\N{\fs12}Well, I guess it makes sense.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.13,0:18:29.04,Default,,0,0,0,,好的  那我去安排下\N{\fs12}Okay, I'll schedule it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.16,0:18:32.29,Default,,0,0,0,,明天早上9点  奥尼克斯的人会\N{\fs12}Tomorrow morning at 9, the guys from Onyx
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.42,0:18:34.27,Default,,0,0,0,,去办公室谈合并的事情\N{\fs12}are coming over to the office to talk over the merger.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.40,0:18:35.96,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道  我来安排会议\N{\fs12}I know. I set the meeting.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.09,0:18:37.68,Default,,0,0,0,,好\N{\fs12}Hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.81,0:18:41.26,Default,,0,0,0,,我觉得这次会议的关键是保留条款\N{\fs12}I think the key is that hold-back provision.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.39,0:18:43.75,Default,,0,0,0,,富勒会尽可能把钱托管\N{\fs12}Fuller's gonna want to keep as much money in escrow as--
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.88,0:18:46.15,Default,,0,0,0,,爸\N{\fs12}Dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.21,0:18:48.00,Default,,0,0,0,,我会处理的\N{\fs12}Just let me deal with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.31,0:18:50.97,Default,,0,0,0,,好的  好吧\N{\fs12}Yeah, right.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.09,0:18:55.63,Default,,0,0,0,,你跟他们说我有些私事要处理\N{\fs12}Maybe let's just tell them I got some personal situation to take care of.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.75,0:18:57.64,Default,,0,0,0,,- 私事  - 是啊\N{\fs12}- Personal situation? - Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.76,0:18:59.94,Default,,0,0,0,,不要什么都告诉他们\N{\fs12}Just... be vague.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.06,0:19:01.31,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么\N{\fs12}Why not just tell the truth?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.44,0:19:03.32,Default,,0,0,0,,他们有可能会解雇我们\N{\fs12}They might fire us.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.02,0:19:09.51,Default,,0,0,0,,尼古拉斯  我不是想侮辱你\N{\fs12}Nicholas, I'm not trying to insult you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.64,0:19:12.23,Default,,0,0,0,,我已经给富勒打过三场案子了\N{\fs12}I've closed three deals for Fuller.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.35,0:19:15.74,Default,,0,0,0,,我也为他工作了5年了  他知道我是什么样的律师\N{\fs12}I've worked for him for five years. He knows what kind of lawyer I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.87,0:19:18.07,Default,,0,0,0,,- 好  - 好吧\N{\fs12}- Right. - Right, well...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.66,0:19:21.79,Default,,0,0,0,,不要把话说死\N{\fs12}Be vague.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.35,0:19:36.73,Default,,0,0,0,,他怎么样了\N{\fs12}How is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.86,0:19:38.74,Default,,0,0,0,,他们给他安排了明天的手术\N{\fs12}They scheduled his surgery for tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.87,0:19:41.85,Default,,0,0,0,,不妨就把病都治好\N{\fs12}Might as well get it over with.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.98,0:19:43.83,Default,,0,0,0,,对啊\N{\fs12}Exactly.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.96,0:19:46.46,Default,,0,0,0,,- 嗨  - 嗨\N{\fs12}- Hi. - Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.58,0:19:47.99,Default,,0,0,0,,饿了吗\N{\fs12}You hungry?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.12,0:19:49.91,Default,,0,0,0,,不饿\N{\fs12}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.04,0:19:52.35,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧  我给你准备了一把新的牙刷\N{\fs12}All right. Well, I put a new toothbrush for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.47,0:19:53.72,Default,,0,0,0,,就在大厅那边的洗手间里\N{\fs12}lt's in the bathroom down the hall over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.85,0:19:56.31,Default,,0,0,0,,那里还有毛巾  肥皂  沐浴露\N{\fs12}And there's towels and soap and shampoo and all that.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.44,0:19:58.74,Default,,0,0,0,,我在书房的沙发上给你铺了床\N{\fs12}I pulled out the sofa bed for you, too, in the den.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.87,0:20:01.63,Default,,0,0,0,,铺得不好  不好意思\N{\fs12}lt's kinda lumpy though. Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.75,0:20:03.54,Default,,0,0,0,,还有什么\N{\fs12}What else?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.67,0:20:05.62,Default,,0,0,0,,你要不要子在上学前稍微睡一会儿\N{\fs12}Do you want to try and get some sleep before school?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.75,0:20:07.26,Default,,0,0,0,,我今天能不能待在家\N{\fs12}Can't I just stay home today?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.38,0:20:08.92,Default,,0,0,0,,不行  我们得工作\N{\fs12}No, we have to work.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.05,0:20:11.42,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧\N{\fs12}Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.49,0:20:15.70,Default,,0,0,0,,伯顿会不会死啊\N{\fs12}ls Burton gonna die?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.83,0:20:18.07,Default,,0,0,0,,不会  他\N{\fs12}No, he...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.51,0:20:20.92,Default,,0,0,0,,如果他死了\N{\fs12}lf he dies--
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.05,0:20:23.59,Default,,0,0,0,,香农  能不能不要说了  他不会死的  好吗\N{\fs12}Shannon, could you just stop it? He's not gonna die, okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.71,0:20:58.30,Default,,0,0,0,,我跟克伦威尔・斯温的马特・邓恩聊过了\N{\fs12}I spoke to Matt Dunn at Cromwell-Swain.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.43,0:21:00.64,Default,,0,0,0,,你爸不来开会了吗\N{\fs12}Your father's not coming to this meeting?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.76,0:21:04.50,Default,,0,0,0,,不来了  所以  邓恩说保留条款没有问题\N{\fs12}No. So Dunn is okay with the hold-back provision. He says no problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.63,0:21:06.96,Default,,0,0,0,,他没跟我说他今天不来\N{\fs12}He didn't tell me that he wasn't coming to this meeting.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.09,0:21:09.39,Default,,0,0,0,,他有私事要处理\N{\fs12}He has a personal situation to attend to.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.52,0:21:12.20,Default,,0,0,0,,在12页上  我们可以看到\N{\fs12}On page 12, you will see that the--
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.33,0:21:14.02,Default,,0,0,0,,等等  等等\N{\fs12}Wait. Wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.15,0:21:17.95,Default,,0,0,0,,什么意思  什么私事\N{\fs12}What do you mean, a personal situation?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.08,0:21:19.58,Default,,0,0,0,,私事\N{\fs12}A personal situation.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.46,0:21:23.35,Default,,0,0,0,,你们能不能出去一下\N{\fs12}You guys want to gives us a minute here?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.48,0:21:25.62,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢\N{\fs12}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.33,0:21:30.12,Default,,0,0,0,,这不像伯顿\N{\fs12}This doesn't sound like Burton.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.25,0:21:32.55,Default,,0,0,0,,伯顿从1978年以来就没有缺席过会议\N{\fs12}urton hasn't missed a meeting since 19T8.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.68,0:21:34.63,Default,,0,0,0,,发生什么事了\N{\fs12}What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.77,0:21:38.85,Default,,0,0,0,,他健康出了点问题\N{\fs12}He has a medical issue.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.97,0:21:40.09,Default,,0,0,0,,什么问题\N{\fs12}What kind of medical issue?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.22,0:21:43.23,Default,,0,0,0,,- 心脏  - 心脏\N{\fs12}- Heart. - Heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.43,0:21:48.69,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧  那我们还是等他回到办公室再谈这件事吧\N{\fs12}Okay. So listen, why don't we just wait until he gets back to the office
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.82,0:21:50.25,Default,,0,0,0,,我们再接着说这件事\N{\fs12}and then we'll just finish this up then?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.38,0:21:51.24,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你确定吗  - 我确定\N{\fs12}- You sure? - Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.37,0:21:53.42,Default,,0,0,0,,- 好吗  - 好吧\N{\fs12}- Okay? - All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.54,0:21:55.69,Default,,0,0,0,,- 哪个医院  - 匹兹堡纪念医院\N{\fs12}- What hospital? - Pittsburgh Memorial.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.81,0:21:58.69,Default,,0,0,0,,对  我明白  胡特医生事世界顶尖的医生\N{\fs12}Yeah, I understand Hutter's world-class.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.57,0:22:10.16,Default,,0,0,0,,结果  训练营的一个辅导员就一拳打在他脸上了\N{\fs12}As a result, a camp counselor punched him in the face
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.29,0:22:11.37,Default,,0,0,0,,并且用手电筒袭击了他\N{\fs12}and hit him with a flashlight.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.50,0:22:13.45,Default,,0,0,0,,缝了七针  身上都是伤\N{\fs12}Seven stitches and bruised ribs.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.58,0:22:15.24,Default,,0,0,0,,法官大人  请看看我的当事人\N{\fs12}Now take a look at my client, Your Honor.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.37,0:22:18.95,Default,,0,0,0,,很显然  他不适合待在那里\N{\fs12}This is clearly not a good fit.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.64,0:22:21.89,Default,,0,0,0,,我们会给他转到新的地方\N{\fs12}We'll move him.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.01,0:22:23.90,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢\N{\fs12}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.02,0:22:27.32,Default,,0,0,0,,克里斯今天结束再训练营的时间\N{\fs12}Chris completed 70 days at Summit.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.45,0:22:29.14,Default,,0,0,0,,我推荐给他结业证书\N{\fs12}I recommend that he be given his certificate
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.27,0:22:30.58,Default,,0,0,0,,将他转到紧急收容所\N{\fs12}and placed in an emergency shelter.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.70,0:22:32.01,Default,,0,0,0,,可以\N{\fs12}Fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.14,0:22:36.04,Default,,0,0,0,,但是  监狱他之前的罪行\N{\fs12}But given the seriousness of Chris' previous omenses,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.10,0:22:39.30,Default,,0,0,0,,你要安排对他24小时的监督\N{\fs12}you'll need to arrange 24-hour supervision.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.43,0:22:44.89,Default,,0,0,0,,在我惹事之前  我一直待在一个地方\N{\fs12}There's this place I used to live, before I got in trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.02,0:22:46.26,Default,,0,0,0,,也许我能去那里\N{\fs12}Maybe I could go there.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.39,0:22:47.48,Default,,0,0,0,,不行的\N{\fs12}That's not gonna work.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.61,0:22:49.85,Default,,0,0,0,,但是我很喜欢待在那里  而且那儿的辅导员也喜欢我\N{\fs12}But I liked it there a lot, and the head counselor liked me.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.97,0:22:51.86,Default,,0,0,0,,- 尼克  行不行  - 没得选\N{\fs12}- Nick? - It's not an option.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.98,0:22:53.45,Default,,0,0,0,,你们能不能带我去见我妈\N{\fs12}Could one of you take me to go see my mom?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.58,0:22:55.47,Default,,0,0,0,,你去了收容所肯定会安排的\N{\fs12}I'm sure something can be arranged when you get to the shelter.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.59,0:22:57.70,Default,,0,0,0,,但是我错过了她的生日  她会生气的\N{\fs12}But I missed her birthday, and she'll be upset.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.83,0:23:00.84,Default,,0,0,0,,我错过了她的生日  他们也不带我去见她\N{\fs12}I missed her birthday, and they won't take me to go see her!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.96,0:23:03.58,Default,,0,0,0,,他们会跟训练营一样  答应我带我去  结果没有\N{\fs12}And it'll be just like boot camp, and they'll say they will and they won't!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.71,0:23:05.69,Default,,0,0,0,,他们会忘记我的话  他们不会带我去\N{\fs12}They'll forget, and they won't take me!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.75,0:23:15.50,Default,,0,0,0,,嗨  嗨\N{\fs12}Hi! Hi!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.87,0:23:18.28,Default,,0,0,0,,嗨\N{\fs12}Hi!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.98,0:23:24.67,Default,,0,0,0,,这是我妈妈\N{\fs12}That's my mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.80,0:23:26.36,Default,,0,0,0,,她在睡觉\N{\fs12}She's sleeping.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.49,0:23:28.41,Default,,0,0,0,,也许你应该让她好好睡觉\N{\fs12}Yeah, maybe you should just let her sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.54,0:23:31.64,Default,,0,0,0,,不要  她看到我会很开心的\N{\fs12}No. She'll be excited to see me.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.70,0:23:46.14,Default,,0,0,0,,嗨  妈妈\N{\fs12}Hey, Mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.27,0:23:47.58,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么了\N{\fs12}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.71,0:23:49.82,Default,,0,0,0,,是我  克里斯\N{\fs12}lt's Chris.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.44,0:23:57.93,Default,,0,0,0,,妈妈  妈妈  是我啊\N{\fs12}Ma. Ma, it's Chris.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.06,0:24:00.30,Default,,0,0,0,,我刚在睡觉\N{\fs12}I was sleeping.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.42,0:24:05.41,Default,,0,0,0,,我给你带来了你的生日礼物\N{\fs12}I brought you this card for your birthday.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.54,0:24:08.80,Default,,0,0,0,,我只想睡觉\N{\fs12}I just want to sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.92,0:24:10.81,Default,,0,0,0,,但是我给你带礼物了\N{\fs12}But I brought you this.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.12,0:24:13.43,Default,,0,0,0,,上面写了什么\N{\fs12}What's it say?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.56,0:24:17.84,Default,,0,0,0,,是一首诗\N{\fs12}Um... there's a poem.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.96,0:24:20.11,Default,,0,0,0,,不是我写的\N{\fs12}I didn't write it.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.23,0:24:22.05,Default,,0,0,0,,是他们做卡片的人编的\N{\fs12}Something they made up when they made the cards,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.18,0:24:24.07,Default,,0,0,0,,我在诗的下面写了  生日快乐\N{\fs12}but down here I wrote ''Happy Birthday''
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.19,0:24:28.35,Default,,0,0,0,,还有  我爱你  你是我的好妈妈\N{\fs12}and that I love you and that you're a good mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.41,0:24:30.97,Default,,0,0,0,,你要不要弹一下钢琴\N{\fs12}Are you gonna play the piano?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.10,0:24:33.34,Default,,0,0,0,,不\N{\fs12}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:33.46,0:24:38.07,Default,,0,0,0,,之前有个小孩  时不时会来这里弹琴\N{\fs12}There's a kid... comes here sometimes... plays the piano.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:38.19,0:24:42.54,Default,,0,0,0,,不不  是我  克里斯\N{\fs12}No. No, Mom. It's me. Chris.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:42.66,0:24:45.80,Default,,0,0,0,,我来给你庆生的\N{\fs12}I'm here to celebrate.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:01.45,0:25:05.54,Default,,0,0,0,,我妈之前在一所学校上学  她跟我外婆住\N{\fs12}My mom, she used to go to this school, and she lived with my grandma,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:05.67,0:25:08.35,Default,,0,0,0,,学校旁边有个卖糖果的加油站\N{\fs12}and there's this gas station near the school that sold candy,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:08.48,0:25:10.91,Default,,0,0,0,,她放学回家的路上会去那里\N{\fs12}so she used to go there on her way home.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:11.04,0:25:14.07,Default,,0,0,0,,加油站有个小伙子\N{\fs12}And there was this guy. This, you know, gas station guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:14.20,0:25:15.41,Default,,0,0,0,,额  怎么说来着\N{\fs12}A, um...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:15.54,0:25:17.68,Default,,0,0,0,,- 服务员  - 对\N{\fs12}- Attendant. - Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:17.81,0:25:20.30,Default,,0,0,0,,是的  然后\N{\fs12}Right. And, uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:20.43,0:25:26.03,Default,,0,0,0,,我想他喜欢我妈  我妈然后怀孕就生下了我\N{\fs12}I guess he liked her because she got pregnant and... that's how I was born.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:28.00,0:25:29.66,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧\N{\fs12}Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:31.13,0:25:35.10,Default,,0,0,0,,我想  他应该不愿意承认他是她的男朋友\N{\fs12}But then I guess he didn't really want to admit that he was her boyfriend,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:35.22,0:25:39.38,Default,,0,0,0,,所以  我最后就\N{\fs12}so that's why I ended up...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:39.50,0:25:41.20,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧\N{\fs12}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:43.79,0:25:46.60,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道我妈现在脑子不清楚\N{\fs12}I know my mom's retarded.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:46.72,0:25:49.16,Default,,0,0,0,,但是我不是\N{\fs12}And I know I'm not.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:49.28,0:25:52.86,Default,,0,0,0,,所以你不需要为我感到难过\N{\fs12}So you don't have to feel bad or anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:52.99,0:25:57.82,Default,,0,0,0,,露露  我一直在考虑房子的事情\N{\fs12}You know, I've been thinking, Lulu, about the house.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:57.94,0:25:59.92,Default,,0,0,0,,我要买下它\N{\fs12}I'm gonna buy it.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:02.19,0:26:03.89,Default,,0,0,0,,好啊  我也想尽我的一份力\N{\fs12}Well, I want to contribute what I can.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:04.01,0:26:05.45,Default,,0,0,0,,哪怕只有一点点的分担\N{\fs12}Any percentage of it that I can own--
Dialogue: 0,0:26:05.58,0:26:07.40,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯  只是情况会变得很复杂\N{\fs12}Yeah, it just gets very complicated.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:07.53,0:26:08.93,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我知道  但是我觉得  - 我们想要买下它对不对\N{\fs12}- I know, but I feel-- - We want it, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:09.06,0:26:11.59,Default,,0,0,0,,所以就让我买吧  然后我们再看\N{\fs12}So I'm just going to buy it and then we'll see what happens.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:11.71,0:26:13.82,Default,,0,0,0,,- 再看  - 嗯\N{\fs12}- See what happens? - Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:13.95,0:26:16.92,Default,,0,0,0,,尼克  如果你觉得结婚\N{\fs12}Nick, if you think that... getting married--
Dialogue: 0,0:26:17.05,0:26:18.90,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你觉得这会让事情简单点\N{\fs12}lf you think that that's going to make things easier...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:19.03,0:26:22.45,Default,,0,0,0,,我不是在说结婚的事  我是在说买房子的事情\N{\fs12}No, I'm not talking about marriage. I'm talking about buying a house.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:44.46,0:26:47.40,Default,,0,0,0,,嗨  我醒着呢\N{\fs12}Hey. I'm awake.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:47.53,0:26:50.63,Default,,0,0,0,,我就闭眼眯了一会儿\N{\fs12}Just closed my eyes for a couple a seconds.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:52.74,0:26:54.50,Default,,0,0,0,,你站在这里多久了\N{\fs12}How long you been standing there?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:54.62,0:26:56.89,Default,,0,0,0,,刚到\N{\fs12}I just got here.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:57.02,0:26:59.51,Default,,0,0,0,,坐吧\N{\fs12}Sit down.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:02.68,0:27:06.61,Default,,0,0,0,,富勒今天早上在办公室给我发了一条短信\N{\fs12}I got a message from Fuller this morning at the office.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:06.73,0:27:08.59,Default,,0,0,0,,你是不是告诉他我在医院了\N{\fs12}Did you tell him I was in the hospital?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:08.71,0:27:10.15,Default,,0,0,0,,呃\N{\fs12}Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:10.28,0:27:11.88,Default,,0,0,0,,我必须跟他说实话\N{\fs12}I had to tell him the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:13.99,0:27:15.42,Default,,0,0,0,,尼古拉斯  我跟你说了\N{\fs12}Nicholas, I told you---
Dialogue: 0,0:27:15.55,0:27:16.80,Default,,0,0,0,,爸  我做过合并的案子  我做过很多\N{\fs12}Dad, I've done a merger. I've done dozens of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:16.92,0:27:18.65,Default,,0,0,0,,- 这不是重点  - 那么重点是什么\N{\fs12}- That's not the point. - Then what's the point then?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:18.78,0:27:23.38,Default,,0,0,0,,他可是富勒啊  他身边需要一个固定可靠的律师\N{\fs12}lt's Fuller. He needs a certain kind of attorney at his side.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:28.36,0:27:31.43,Default,,0,0,0,,听着  关于孩子的事情\N{\fs12}Listen, about this baby thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:31.56,0:27:34.85,Default,,0,0,0,,是不是因为孩子你才想结婚的\N{\fs12}ls that why you wanted to get married?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:37.72,0:27:40.54,Default,,0,0,0,,你爱她  我可以看得出来\N{\fs12}Well, you love this woman. I can see that.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:43.76,0:27:46.19,Default,,0,0,0,,你会是个好父亲的\N{\fs12}You'll be a good dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:52.01,0:27:54.60,Default,,0,0,0,,爸  关于奥尼克斯的事我很抱歉\N{\fs12}Listen, I'm sorry about the Onyx deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:56.13,0:27:58.27,Default,,0,0,0,,你想让我怎么做\N{\fs12}What do you want me to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:58.40,0:28:00.22,Default,,0,0,0,,不用做什么\N{\fs12}Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:01.91,0:28:07.92,Default,,0,0,0,,我已经给他打过电话了  我看看能不能搞定\N{\fs12}I'll just call Fuller and see if I can straighten it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:14.02,0:28:15.81,Default,,0,0,0,,嗨  我跟香农说我会去接她的\N{\fs12}Hey. I told Shannon I'd pick her up.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:15.94,0:28:16.83,Default,,0,0,0,,我可以去接她\N{\fs12}I can do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:16.96,0:28:18.30,Default,,0,0,0,,是  但是她想去买化妆品\N{\fs12}Yeah, but she wants to buy makeup.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:18.37,0:28:20.09,Default,,0,0,0,,那好吧\N{\fs12}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:20.22,0:28:21.98,Default,,0,0,0,,另外  那套房子我申请了\N{\fs12}Oh, I made an offer on the house.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:22.11,0:28:24.57,Default,,0,0,0,,- 是吗  - 嗯  申请价格在报价之下\N{\fs12}- You did? - Yeah. TO under the asking.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:24.69,0:28:27.83,Default,,0,0,0,,好的  希望你能买到\N{\fs12}Okay. Well, I hope you get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:27.95,0:28:29.07,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯\N{\fs12}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:29.20,0:28:30.92,Default,,0,0,0,,待会见\N{\fs12}See ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:36.74,0:28:40.00,Default,,0,0,0,,这里好像不允许抽烟\N{\fs12}I know they don't appreciate smoking up here.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:42.11,0:28:43.71,Default,,0,0,0,,你怎么了\N{\fs12}What happened to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:43.83,0:28:46.93,Default,,0,0,0,,我去收容所看望克里斯  他好像在生什么事的气\N{\fs12}I went to see Chris at the shelter. He was upset about something.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:47.06,0:28:49.14,Default,,0,0,0,,生他妈妈的气吗\N{\fs12}His mother?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:49.26,0:28:51.76,Default,,0,0,0,,他一直哭  说了一些关于他妈妈的事\N{\fs12}He was crying. Said something about her.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:51.88,0:28:55.78,Default,,0,0,0,,我把他带到会议室  想要让他冷静下来\N{\fs12}Took him into a meeting room, tried to calm him down.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:55.91,0:28:57.45,Default,,0,0,0,,他打你了吗\N{\fs12}He did this to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:57.57,0:29:01.44,Default,,0,0,0,,他抓住我  打我  骑在我身上\N{\fs12}He grabbed me and hit me and...got on top of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:01.56,0:29:03.93,Default,,0,0,0,,撕掉了我的衬衫\N{\fs12}Ripped my shirt.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:07.80,0:29:09.49,Default,,0,0,0,,幸亏保安来得很快\N{\fs12}Guards came in fast.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:09.62,0:29:11.15,Default,,0,0,0,,你没事吧\N{\fs12}Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:12.65,0:29:14.64,Default,,0,0,0,,我想喝一杯\N{\fs12}I could use a drink.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:19.94,0:29:22.49,Default,,0,0,0,,我跟他想要搬到一起住\N{\fs12}And so we're talking about moving in together,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:22.62,0:29:26.01,Default,,0,0,0,,他跟我将他是一个存在主义者\N{\fs12}and he says to me that he's an existentialist,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:26.14,0:29:29.30,Default,,0,0,0,,他想让我明白什么是存在主义\N{\fs12}and that he wants me to understand what it means.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:29.43,0:29:30.99,Default,,0,0,0,,一直跟我说  意思就是  意识就是\N{\fs12}He keeps saying, ''What it means.''
Dialogue: 0,0:29:31.12,0:29:33.58,Default,,0,0,0,,我就是听不明白\N{\fs12}I don't get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:33.71,0:29:37.96,Default,,0,0,0,,我想  他的意思是让我不要指望他太多\N{\fs12}I think that he meant that he didn't want me to expect too much from him.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:38.09,0:29:42.44,Default,,0,0,0,,这一切都不重要了  那我们为什么还要纠缠下去呢\N{\fs12}Because nothing matters anyway, so why even bother to try.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:42.56,0:29:44.19,Default,,0,0,0,,所以你没有搬去跟他住吗\N{\fs12}So you didn't move in with him?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:44.32,0:29:47.77,Default,,0,0,0,,搬了  但是搬去住简直是一场灾难\N{\fs12}No, I did. It was a disaster.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:54.44,0:29:56.07,Default,,0,0,0,,是不是我拖着你的时间了\N{\fs12}Am I keeping you?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:59.43,0:30:01.57,Default,,0,0,0,,不行\N{\fs12}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:01.70,0:30:05.02,Default,,0,0,0,,我要拖住你\N{\fs12}I'm keeping you.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:08.28,0:30:09.69,Default,,0,0,0,,我喜欢你\N{\fs12}I like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:09.81,0:30:14.13,Default,,0,0,0,,我不需要你对我负责什么的\N{\fs12}I don't care about obligations or whatever.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:14.19,0:30:15.50,Default,,0,0,0,,我都试过了\N{\fs12}I've tried that.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:15.63,0:30:18.28,Default,,0,0,0,,我甚至结过婚\N{\fs12}I even got married for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:18.41,0:30:21.32,Default,,0,0,0,,我只是想\N{\fs12}I just like to...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:21.44,0:30:24.51,Default,,0,0,0,,如果我想感受某件事  我就要去感受\N{\fs12}When I feel something, I like to feel it.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:31.32,0:30:34.87,Default,,0,0,0,,我去跳舞了  你不用一起来\N{\fs12}I'm gonna dance. You don't have to.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:58.22,0:31:01.35,Default,,0,0,0,,能给我一杯龙舌兰吗\N{\fs12}Can I have a shot of tequila?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:10.32,0:32:12.24,Default,,0,0,0,,- 嗨  - 早上好\N{\fs12}- Hi. - Morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:15.61,0:32:17.79,Default,,0,0,0,,我今天可以去医院吗\N{\fs12}May I come to the hospital today?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:17.91,0:32:20.54,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧  需要在医院等很久\N{\fs12}Well, it's just going to be a lot of waiting around.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:20.67,0:32:22.59,Default,,0,0,0,,我想去\N{\fs12}I'd like to come.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:23.72,0:32:25.22,Default,,0,0,0,,那放学之后去吧\N{\fs12}Maybe after school.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:25.35,0:32:28.88,Default,,0,0,0,,我想去  万一  你知道的\N{\fs12}I just want to be there, in case... you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:29.00,0:32:30.16,Default,,0,0,0,,他没事的\N{\fs12}He's gonna be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:30.29,0:32:32.59,Default,,0,0,0,,是的  香农  只是一个很常见的手术\N{\fs12}Yeah, It's just a routine operation, Shannon.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:32.72,0:32:36.44,Default,,0,0,0,,但是如果有意外呢\N{\fs12}But what if something happens?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:36.57,0:32:37.92,Default,,0,0,0,,那我们会解决的\N{\fs12}Then we'll deal with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:38.04,0:32:41.73,Default,,0,0,0,,好  但是如果有什么坏事发生呢  我怎么办\N{\fs12}Right, but if something goes wrong, what's gonna happen to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:41.86,0:32:43.01,Default,,0,0,0,,我住哪儿\N{\fs12}Where will I live?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:43.14,0:32:45.86,Default,,0,0,0,,我们会找到地方住的\N{\fs12}We'll find a place.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:45.99,0:32:47.56,Default,,0,0,0,,但是我不会跟你住是吧\N{\fs12}But not with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:47.69,0:32:49.71,Default,,0,0,0,,我不知道\N{\fs12}I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:54.16,0:32:56.57,Default,,0,0,0,,我十一点半去接你  好吗\N{\fs12}I'll pick you up at 11 :30, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:56.69,0:32:59.52,Default,,0,0,0,,- 拜拜  - 拜拜\N{\fs12}- Bye. - Bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:59.64,0:33:01.50,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我需要一个请假条  - 什么\N{\fs12}- I'll need a note. - What?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:01.63,0:33:04.45,Default,,0,0,0,,离校的话要写请假条\N{\fs12}To get out of school. I'll need a note.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:04.51,0:33:06.44,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧\N{\fs12}All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:11.82,0:33:14.36,Default,,0,0,0,,老师叫玛莎卡\N{\fs12}Miss Mashaka.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:25.44,0:33:27.34,Default,,0,0,0,,- 嗨  - 嗨\N{\fs12}- Hey. - Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:27.46,0:33:30.12,Default,,0,0,0,,我昨天跟你父亲在电话里聊过了\N{\fs12}I spoke with your dad on the phone yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:30.25,0:33:31.60,Default,,0,0,0,,听起来他状态不错\N{\fs12}Sounds like he's doing pretty good.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:31.73,0:33:33.62,Default,,0,0,0,,是  目前他身体状况还可以\N{\fs12}Yeah, he's doing great, given the circumstances.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:33.74,0:33:36.21,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯  我们都知道伯顿是个硬汉\N{\fs12}Well, we both know that Burton is tough.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:36.34,0:33:38.17,Default,,0,0,0,,但是这件事是等不到他\N{\fs12}But there's no way that he's gonna get back to this office
Dialogue: 0,0:33:38.30,0:33:40.70,Default,,0,0,0,,回来再结解决了\N{\fs12}in time to close this up.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:40.83,0:33:42.50,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊  如您所知  富勒先生\N{\fs12}Right. Well, as you know, Mr. Fuller,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:42.62,0:33:44.61,Default,,0,0,0,,我很擅长做合并的案子\N{\fs12}I'm perfectly capable of doing this kind of work myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:44.74,0:33:45.64,Default,,0,0,0,,是\N{\fs12}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:45.76,0:33:47.27,Default,,0,0,0,,我雇了兰达尔・柯克的公司\N{\fs12}I hired Randall Kirk's firm.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:49.35,0:33:50.80,Default,,0,0,0,,兰达尔・柯克\N{\fs12}Randall Kirk.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:50.92,0:33:52.88,Default,,0,0,0,,他会接受这个案子的\N{\fs12}He's gonna be taking over this deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:53.01,0:33:54.93,Default,,0,0,0,,好的\N{\fs12}Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:55.06,0:34:00.32,Default,,0,0,0,,你能不能把资料交给他  跟他把事情的进展交代清楚\N{\fs12}So, if you could get him the files and bring him up to speed?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:01.92,0:34:03.45,Default,,0,0,0,,当然\N{\fs12}Yeah. Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:03.58,0:34:05.19,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢\N{\fs12}Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:29.38,0:34:30.76,Default,,0,0,0,,嗨\N{\fs12}Hi.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:30.89,0:34:33.46,Default,,0,0,0,,我找尼克・法林\N{\fs12}I'm here to see Nick Fallin.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:41.76,0:34:43.04,Default,,0,0,0,,嗨\N{\fs12}Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:53.07,0:34:55.02,Default,,0,0,0,,嗨\N{\fs12}Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:55.15,0:35:00.38,Default,,0,0,0,,我\N{\fs12}l...just...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:00.44,0:35:02.97,Default,,0,0,0,,克里斯昨晚从收容所跑掉了\N{\fs12}Chris ran away from the shelter last night.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:22.11,0:35:24.03,Default,,0,0,0,,我要被送到教改所了是吧\N{\fs12}I'm going to Juvie, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:30.79,0:35:34.13,Default,,0,0,0,,我有种感觉\N{\fs12}I have these feelings...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:34.25,0:35:37.11,Default,,0,0,0,,一直以来  关于女生\N{\fs12}all the time... about girls.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:40.73,0:35:44.13,Default,,0,0,0,,我一看到她们  我就\N{\fs12}And when I see them, I just...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:45.92,0:35:47.55,Default,,0,0,0,,我不知道  我\N{\fs12}I don't know, l...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:47.68,0:35:52.81,Default,,0,0,0,,我只是有种感觉  她们让我不舒服\N{\fs12}I just have these feelings, and they don't make me feel very good.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:57.90,0:36:03.00,Default,,0,0,0,,我不是故意伤害她或者是吓到她的\N{\fs12}I didn't mean to hurt her... or scare her.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:03.13,0:36:05.05,Default,,0,0,0,,我只是\N{\fs12}I just...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:07.23,0:36:09.70,Default,,0,0,0,,我只是想碰碰她\N{\fs12}I just wanted to touch her.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:11.65,0:36:13.03,Default,,0,0,0,,我们走吧  克里斯\N{\fs12}Let's go, Chris.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:27.10,0:36:29.02,Default,,0,0,0,,我们走\N{\fs12}Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:40.08,0:36:42.30,Default,,0,0,0,,嗨  你怎么样了\N{\fs12}Hey. How you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:42.42,0:36:44.60,Default,,0,0,0,,我很好  你呢\N{\fs12}I'm good. I'm good. And you?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:44.73,0:36:48.03,Default,,0,0,0,,还不知道\N{\fs12}We'll see.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:50.69,0:36:53.13,Default,,0,0,0,,爸  一切都会好起来的\N{\fs12}Dad, it's all gonna be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:53.25,0:36:56.75,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊\N{\fs12}Yeah, well...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:56.81,0:36:58.38,Default,,0,0,0,,对\N{\fs12}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:01.75,0:37:04.60,Default,,0,0,0,,我  呃\N{\fs12}l, uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:37:07.87,0:37:11.17,Default,,0,0,0,,我只是  你知道的\N{\fs12}I just... you know...
Dialogue: 0,0:37:11.30,0:37:12.81,Default,,0,0,0,,我高兴你做手术了\N{\fs12}I'm glad you're doing this.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:12.93,0:37:15.75,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯\N{\fs12}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:19.54,0:37:21.27,Default,,0,0,0,,富勒跟兰达尔・柯克签约了\N{\fs12}Fuller signed with Randall Kirk.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:21.39,0:37:22.97,Default,,0,0,0,,他告诉我了\N{\fs12}He told me.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:23.09,0:37:24.66,Default,,0,0,0,,我试过挽回他  但是\N{\fs12}Yeah, I tried to get him back but...
Dialogue: 0,0:37:24.79,0:37:26.71,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道  我知道\N{\fs12}I know. I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:33.25,0:37:37.58,Default,,0,0,0,,尼古拉斯  听着  手术没问题的\N{\fs12}Nicholas, look, this is not gonna be a problem, this operation.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:37.71,0:37:39.76,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道  我知道\N{\fs12}I know. I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:39.89,0:37:43.13,Default,,0,0,0,,你没什么好担心的  没事的\N{\fs12}lt's nothing for you to worry about. It's just... nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:44.98,0:37:46.91,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯\N{\fs12}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:23.28,0:38:26.39,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯  好的  好吧\N{\fs12}Yeah, fine. Right. Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:28.95,0:38:31.04,Default,,0,0,0,,刚才是潘妮打过来的\N{\fs12}That was Penny.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:31.17,0:38:32.96,Default,,0,0,0,,是吗\N{\fs12}Oh, yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:33.09,0:38:36.10,Default,,0,0,0,,是  他们拒绝了我的报价\N{\fs12}Yeah. They rejected the offer.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:40.14,0:38:42.58,Default,,0,0,0,,你要不要再跟他们谈谈\N{\fs12}You gonna counter?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:42.70,0:38:43.95,Default,,0,0,0,,不用了\N{\fs12}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:46.36,0:38:48.28,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧\N{\fs12}Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:58.22,0:38:59.95,Default,,0,0,0,,你一定非常累了\N{\fs12}You must be exhausted.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:00.07,0:39:03.12,Default,,0,0,0,,不  没有\N{\fs12}No, not really.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:03.25,0:39:05.65,Default,,0,0,0,,你出门的时候很晚了\N{\fs12}Well, you were out so late.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:05.78,0:39:07.67,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊\N{\fs12}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:07.80,0:39:10.72,Default,,0,0,0,,发生什么事了\N{\fs12}What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:11.87,0:39:15.36,Default,,0,0,0,,我跟你说过  那个小孩  克里斯  他袭击了社会工作员\N{\fs12}I told you. That kid, Chris, he attacked the social worker.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:15.49,0:39:17.93,Default,,0,0,0,,- 苏珊娜  - 是的\N{\fs12}- Suzanne. - Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:18.06,0:39:20.20,Default,,0,0,0,,揍得不轻\N{\fs12}Beat her up.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:57.09,0:39:58.79,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么样了\N{\fs12}How'd it go?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:58.92,0:40:00.78,Default,,0,0,0,,四条堵塞的动脉都搞定了\N{\fs12}Well, we got all four arteries.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:00.91,0:40:02.61,Default,,0,0,0,,所以他没事了是吗\N{\fs12}So he's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:02.73,0:40:04.02,Default,,0,0,0,,手术很成功\N{\fs12}It went well.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:04.14,0:40:07.48,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢你  谢谢\N{\fs12}Oh, thank you. Thank you.
